She beats up one student earlier on in the show and later gets into it with his brother. She can easily hold her own but when it comes to her "feelings" She doesn't mind not really fighting back. But anyway this DVD is a great H-series I loved watching it. It arrived earlier than expected. Thanks Right Stuf. You guys always come through for me. Anyway this is a great show and I would recommend it for anyone who likes H-Series.
